cast.overview: Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.
cast.title: Barbie

details.biography: Isla Ashworth is a British actress. She can be seen in BARBIE alongside Margot Robbie & Ryan Gosling directed by Greta Gerwig. She has also recently wrapped on HERE, directed by Robert Zemeckis, and acting alongside Tom Hanks and Robin Wright. She can be heard on the cult favourite SUMMER CAMP ISLAND voicing Young Mildred, including singing an adorable song. Isla has also featured in many adverts and voiceovers for various high-profile brands.
details.name: Isla Ashworth
